    <h1>1. Santorini, Greece</h1>
    <img src="images/ourpicks_santorini.jpg" width ="600" height= "700" alt="Santorini. " />
  <br>
    <h3>Reasons to visit</h3>
    <li> Great beaches.</li>
    <li> Vivid buildings and houses.</li>
    <li> Great place in Europe for Honeymoons.</li>
  <br>
      <h3>What makes Santorini a great place to visit?</h3>
      <p>Santorini has been our favorite for a tremendously long time. You will enjoy the vivid colors radiating from the houses 
        near the coast and the refreshing waves splashing over the rocks. This place has topped our expectations for traveling and 
        enjoying the scenic atmosphere. The weather is exceptionally ideal all throughout the year making this a great place to visit 
        any time of the year. If you are a health conscious person, the mediterranean diet is very healthy consisting of fish, olive oil, 
        fresh vegitables, and much more. We highly recommend visiting Santorini for your next vacation, you will not regret it.
      </p>
  </ul>
