    <h1>2. Zurich, Switzerland</h1>
    <img src="images/ourpicks_zurich.jpg" width ="600" height= "700" alt="Zurich. " />
    <br>
    <h3>Reasons to visit</h3>
    <li> Picturesque mountinous landscapes. </li>
    <li> Great place for people that like very cold winters.</li>
  <br>
      <h3>What makes Zurich a great place to visit?</h3>
      <p>The Swiss city of Zurich perfectly captures the scene of a city that is surrounded by snow covered mountains.
        You will definitely enjoy Zurich for the fun activities you can do inside the city and outside. Inside the city 
        you can enjoy the swiss architecture and observe the intricate the roads mode from cobblestones. While your in the
        city, be sure to try the Swiss chocolates they sell in the local candy shops, you will be amazed! If you decide to
        venture outside of the city snowboading, sking and hiking are all great activities to do outside of the city.
      </p>
