  <!-- Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada Section-->
  <ul>
    <h1>3. Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada</h1>
    <img src="images/ourpicks_vancouver.jpg" width ="600" height= "700" alt="Vancouver. " />
    <br>
    <h3>Reasons to visit</h3>
    <li> Awesome place for sking or snowboarding.</li>
    <li> Great parks to visit.</li>
    <li> Very active city life.</li>
    <br>
      <h3>What makes Vancouver a great place to visit?</h3>
      <p> Vancouver is a youthful and energetic city. There is basically everything that a tourist can do while traveling here. 
        They can go skiing and snowboading on the snowy mountains. If your on a mood to explore the parks, try visiting Stanley park
        and enjoy the outdoors while you are there. If you want to the view wonderful landscapes, you can visit Queen Elizabeth park 
        and and enjoy the spectacular variety of trees, shurbs, and colorful flowers. The city is filled with wonderful restaurants,
        malls, and entertainment. Visit Vancouver on your next traveling journey!

      </p>
  </ul>
