  <!-- Maldives Section-->
  <ul>
    <h1>4. Maldives</h1>
    <img src="images/ourpicks_maldives.jpg" width ="600" height= "700" alt="Maldives. " />
    <br>
    <h3>Reasons to visit</h3>
    <li> Great for underwater activites. </li>
    <li> Has one of the best beaches in the world. </li>
    <li> It is one of the best honeymoon spots.</li>
    <br>
      <h3>What makes Maldives a great place to visit?</h3>
      <p> The island of the Maldives is a extremely refreshing place to visit on your next vacation with
        with friends, family, or a loved one. If you enjoy the sea life and underwater activites, this place
        exceeds the criteria for anyone who enjoys underwater exploration. The orange horizon during the sunset is 
        seen clearly, almost like if you are watching it from a movie scene. During the night, the beaches glow 
        with bright blue specs, which is a natural phenomenon! The reason why it glows is mainly due to the bioluminescent
        plakton washed up on the shores. Therefore, radiating a bluish glow on the wet sand where the waves retrieve.
        Come to Maldives, you will enjoy every bit of the moments you spend here!
        
      </p>
  </ul>
