  <!-- Cappadocia, Turkey Section-->
  <ul>
    <h1>5. Cappadocia, Turkey</h1>
    <img src="images/ourpicks_cappadocia.jpg" width ="600" height= "700" alt="Cappadocia. " />
    <br>
    <h3>Reasons to visit</h3>
    <li> Fairy-tale like atmosphere.</li>
    <li> Fun activities such as hot air balloon rides.</li>
    <li> Great weather.</li>
    <br>
      <h3>What makes Cappadocia a great place to visit?</h3>
      <p> Cappadocia will encapsulate one of the most spectacular scenes that you will ever see in the course of your life. 
        This interesting spot resembles something you would see on another planet, yet it is in Turkey. During your visit to 
        Cappadocia, you have the occasion to encounter this wonderful land without any limits. There are hot air balloons filling 
        the skyline and demonstrating a spectacle that is extremely rare and like a picturesque movie. The unique rock formations 
        create a natural form of art while the sky is in the background. There are also some interesting and intricate caves and 
        ruins built into the rock formations, which add another touch to this fairy-tale like destination. If you are an adventurous
        person, you will certainly enjoy Cappadocia.
      </p>
  </ul>
